description: This file declares interface functions related to VLAN manager APIs used for bus utility operations, such as retrieving parameter values of different types and obtaining instance numbers by index. It is part of a larger system dealing with network configuration and management.
external_files: possibly included elsewhere in the project for types like ULONG, BOOL, PULONG, but not explicitly shown here

methods.name: GetParamValueUlong
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long value for a given parameter name.

methods.name: GetParamValueString
methods.description: Retrieves a string value for a given parameter name, with buffer and size handling.

methods.name: GetParamValueBool
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean value for a given parameter name.

methods.name: GetInstanceNumberByIndex
methods.description: Returns an instance number corresponding to a given object name and index.
